      '2. Breathe. It sounds trivial, but it works on a physiological level: a long exhale, twice as long as the inhale, switches the nervous system into a calm mode in about a minute. Open the breathing practice in the app, or just do 10 slow exhales, counting silently. Inhale for 4 — exhale for 8.',
